{"created": "2026-03-25T12:21:35.468490", "current_version": "1.0.0", "project": "ESP32 Distance Sensor", "versions": {"1.0.0": {"created": "2026-03-25T12:21:35.468488", "creator": {"program": "sphinx_needs", "version": "8.0.0"}, "needs": {"SPEC_SNS_ISR_1": {"acceptance_criteria": "", "api_signature": "", "arch": {}, "avatar": null, "closed_at": null, "completion": null, "component": "", "constraints": [], "constraints_error": null, "constraints_passed": true, "constraints_results": {}, "content": "**Design:** IRAM-resident ISR for deterministic timestamp capture.\n\n**Implementation:**\n\n- Rising edge: Capture ``echo_start_time`` using ``esp_timer_get_time()``\n- Falling edge: Capture ``echo_end_time`` and queue raw measurement via ``xQueueSendFromISR``\n- Uses ``portYIELD_FROM_ISR`` for task scheduling\n- Marked ``IRAM_ATTR`` for real-time constraints\n- No floating-point, heap allocation, or blocking operations\n\n**Validation:** ISR execution time < 10\u00b5s, timestamps captured accurately, raw queue\nreceives data.", "created_at": null, "docname": "12_design/spec_distance_sensor", "doctype": ".rst", "duration": null, "external_css": "external_link", "external_url": null, "has_dead_links": false, "has_forbidden_dead_links": false, "header_file": "", "id": "SPEC_SNS_ISR_1", "id_prefix": null, "is_external": false, "is_import": false, "is_modified": false, "jinja_content": false, "layout": null, "lineno": 56, "links": ["REQ_SNS_3", "REQ_SNS_8"], "links_back": [], "max_amount": null, "max_content_lines": null, "modifications": 0, "parameters": "", "params": null, "parent_need": null, "parent_needs": [], "parent_needs_back": [], "parts": {}, "post_content": null, "post_template": null, "pre_content": null, "pre_template": null, "prefix": null, "priority": "", "query": null, "rationale": "", "returns": "", "section_name": "Architecture Specifications", "sections": ["Architecture Specifications", "Distance Sensor Design Specification"], "service": null, "signature":